"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-2141775-Andy-Murray-trophies-Olympic-medals\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murraywon everything possible during his glittering career, claiming 46 titles - including three Grand Slams, two Olympic gold medals, and 14 Masters 1000s.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit also reached the top of the rankings and received the year-end No.\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 trophy in 2016.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that he's been retired for more than a year, some would assume that Murray's silverware has extra meaning to him - but the 38-year-old has revealed that he's no longer as protective of his Olympic medals, even letting his children \\\"scratch\\\" them.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8942119986828738e-16, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray's trophies still have their own designated spot in his home - courtesy of his wife, Kim's handiwork.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8942119986828738e-16, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9991446029215769, \"rank\": 0.0007837731738862641, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the two-timeWimbledonchampion is not fussed about spending time with his hard-earned cups.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we moved house my wife made like a trophy cabinet.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's downstairs, out the way but yeah, there is one in there.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is pretty big, it's a decent size.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But actually, I mean, I am fine with them being in there, but I do not go and look at them daily.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something that I think about loads,\\\" the former world No.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 told the Tennis Podcast.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Murray is not enamoured by his trophies, he used to treat his two Olympic gold medals like a prized possession.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8942119986828738e-16, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One had been on display at the Wimbledon museum until very recently.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But nowadays, the Brit is a little more careless with his London and Rio golds - and his four children have more fun with them than he does.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.99999999091483, \"rank\": 8.395096738483304e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I actually got it back last week.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It had been in there for, I think, about a year, but yeah, I got it back recently.\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic medals, yeah, they are in there [the cabinet].\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I ever wear them?\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My kids wear them sometimes, yeah.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was quite precious about them in the beginning, but now I am like, 'Whatever, it's fine.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scratch them up and stuff, whatever'.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them wanted to take one of them into school, I do not know what it was.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were doing something at school and we were like, no, that's a bit much to send them in with one of them.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we gave them my Beijing Olympics participation medal instead, which they were happy with.\\\"\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9631140358713625, \"rank\": 0.03829773674073365, \"text\": \"Beijing Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray might not be so careful with his medals, but the three-time Major winner has some other important Olympics mementos in his home - the famous Olympic pins.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8942119986828738e-16, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During his farewell tournament at the Paris 2024 Games, the Brit went out of his way to collect as many rare pins as possible.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he's now been left wondering whether it was worth it.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I have still got all of them, yeah.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have kept all of them.\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was something that, at the time, I absolutely loved doing it every single Olympics whereas now I am a bit like, did I sort of spend a bit too much time walking around the village and stopping at different tables in the restaurant?\\\"\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he laughed.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just like, oh, that guy is from Eritrea, that's a rare pin.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 